    <title>Html/CSS启蒙</title>
    <url>/pigz2538.github.io/2020/05/04/Html-CSS%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1><span id="发现个学习htmlcss的好网站">发现个学习Html/CSS的好网站</span></h1><p>就这个<br><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.w3school.com.cn/</a></p>
<p><img src= data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs= data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pigz2538/Images/Images/20200504225723.png" alt></p>
<p>看起来挺爽的，查资料啥的也方便，主要有时候markdown语法和网页渲染冲突啥的，比如<span style="border-bottom:2px solid red;">下划线</span>。</p>
<div class="hide-block"><a class="hide-button button--primary button--animated" style>如何实现下划线？
    </a><span class="hide-content"><p>上边这个是这样实现的：<br><code>&lt;span style=&quot;border-bottom:2px solid red;&quot;&gt;下划线&lt;/span&gt;</code></p><p>实际上是巧用了CSS的边框，还有多种可供选择。</p><p><img src= data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs= data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pigz2538/Images/Images/20200504225719.png" alt></p></span></div>



]]></content>
